tine-age-reverse-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20%242%20million%20a%20year%20to%20feel%2018%20again%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20has%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20fix%20for%20his%20achy%2C%2046-year-old%20knees%20and%20hips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20claims%20he%20finally%20has%20a%20solution%3A%20flying%20to%20the%20Bahamas%20for%20an%20experimental%20therapy%20to%20have%20millions%20of%20stem%20cells%20from%20healthy%20young%20Swedish%20volunteers%20injected%20into%20his%20knees%2C%20hips%2C%20and%20shoulders.%20The%20price%20tag%3F%20About%20%2416%2C500%20per%20joint%2C%20or%20a%20whole-body%20combo%20for%20%2425%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20new%20science%3B%20stem%20cell%20therapy%20research%20has%20already%20shown%20promise%20as%20a%20potential%20treatment%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC9276428%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaging-related%20ailments%20such%20as%20diabetes%20to%20heart%20disease%2C%20and%20arthritis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20using%20it%20to%20limber%20up%20the%20knees%20of%20healthy%20(and%20wealthy)%2040-somethings%20is%20new%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Johnson%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20taking%20advantage%20of%20this%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wellness%20industry%20is%20buzzing%20with%20furtive%20excitement%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20rejuvenating%20knees%20with%20a%20shot%20of%20young%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20FDA-approved%20in%20the%20US%2C%20some%20clinics%20abroad%20are%20able%20to%20provide%20the%20treatments%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20regulatory%20agencies%20in%20other%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20price.%20A%20massive%20market%20of%20unregulated%20clinics%20are%20already%20cashing%20in%20on%20consumer%20interest%20in%20the%20therapeutic%20power%20of%20stem%20cells%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%241%2C200%20to%20%2428%2C000%20per%20treatment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1934590921004203%23bib3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20in%20the%20longevity%20field%20say%20this%20is%20a%20promising%20idea%2C%20and%20experiments%20like%20Johnson's%20may%20even%20help%20to%20nudge%20the%20healthcare%20paradigm%20toward%20proactive%2C%20preventive%20care%20for%20our%20joints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20here's%20what%20we%20know%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20we%20don't%20know%20%E2%80%94%20about%20stem%20cell%20therapy%20for%20knees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8a87341-02d0-4d86-93d4-5ba542d5f280%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20shot%20to%20supercharge%20the%20body's%20natural%20healing%20ability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Johnson's%20pursuit%20of%20%26quot%3Bsuperhero%20joints%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20flew%20to%20Physical%20Longevity%2C%20the%20Bahamian%20clinic%20that%20is%20developing%20experimental%20anti-aging%20treatments%2C%20largely%20with%20stem%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20didn't%20want%20just%20any%20stem%20cells.%20Johnson%20booked%20a%20specific%20type%20of%20treatment%20involving%20%3Cem%3Emesenchymal%20stem%20cells%3C%2Fem%3E%20(or%2C%20MSCs).%20These%20cells%20are%20all%20the%20rage%20in%20longevity%20circles%20these%20days%20because%20they%20seem%20to%20reduce%20inflammation%20and%20promote%20regeneration.%20Unlike%20other%20cells%2C%20they%20can%20act%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20isolated%20from%20other%20tissues%2C%20naturally%20gravitating%20toward%20injured%20or%20dysfunctional%20tissues%20to%20help%20repair%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Fjournals%2Fbioengineering-and-biotechnology%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffbioe.2020.00043%2Ffull%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Esuggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20BI%20about%20a%20month%20after%20his%20procedure%2C%20Johnson%20said%20he%20hasn't%20noticed%20much%20change%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bryan%20Johnson%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e77898a7adf700190714e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221303%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBryan%20Johnson%20flew%20to%20the%20Bahamas%20to%20get%20MSC%20stem%20cells%20injected%20into%20his%20knees%2C%20hips%2C%20and%20shoulders%20%E2%80%94%20for%20about%20%2416%2C500%20per%20joint.%3Cp%3EJosh%20DeAngelis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20probably%20because%20my%20health%20biomarkers%20are%20already%20in%20the%20top%201%25%20as%20far%20as%20muscle%2C%20fat%2C%20metabolic%20health%2C%20cardiovascular%20health%2C%20et%20cetera%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20health%20stats%20shared%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprotocol.bryanjohnson.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20pretty%20difficult%20for%20my%20subjective%20feeling%20of%20wellness%20to%20improve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Johnson%20said%20he's%20waiting%20for%20the%20objective%20data%20to%20see%20the%20benefits%2C%20trusting%20a%20process%20he%20developed%20over%20years%20(with%20millions%20of%20dollars)%20to%20determine%20which%20longevity%20treatments%20are%20worth%20it.%20He%20hired%20a%20team%20of%20medical%20experts%20who%20evaluate%20peer-reviewed%20studies%20on%20potential%20longevity%20treatments%2C%20ranking%20the%20quality%20of%20evidence%2C%20Johnson%20told%20BI.%20MSC%20therapy%20made%20the%20cut%20as%20a%20treatment%20of%20interest%2C%20and%20Johnson%20said%20he%20and%20his%20team%20felt%20the%20clinic%20and%20stem%20cell%20provider%20were%20trustworthy%20and%20safe.%20It%20was%20worth%20making%20the%20trip%20to%20the%20Bahamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20only%20FDA-approved%20stem%20cell%20therapies%20you%20can%20access%20in%20the%20US%20use%20the%20patient's%20own%20cells.%20While%20that's%20effective%20for%20some%20things%2C%20it%20may%20not%20do%20very%20much%20to%20rejuvenate%20your%20joints%2C%20Rasul%20Chaudhry%2C%20professor%20of%20biological%20sciences%20at%20Oakland%20University%20who%20specializes%20in%20stem%20cell%20research%2C%20told%20BI.%20It's%20tough%20to%20reverse%20age-related%20damage%20with%20cells%20that%20have%20aged%20with%20you%2C%20Chaudhry%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYounger%20cells%20drawn%20from%20healthy%20volunteers%20seem%20to%20be%20better%20at%20repairing%20and%20regenerating%20damage%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20that's%20what%20Johnson's%20doctor%2C%20Steven%20Sampson%2C%20told%20BI.%20Chaundhry%20said%20that%20might%20be%20true%2C%20if%20you're%20use%20cells%20from%20an%20embryo%2C%20but%20there%20are%20ethical%20and%20technical%20concerns%20with%20that%2C%20and%20even%20cells%20from%20healthy%2020-something%20donors%20have%20aged%20to%20varying%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20promising%20area%20of%20medicine%2C%20but%20far%20from%20FDA%20approval.%20Plus%2C%20even%20Sampson%20warns%20that%20young%20donor%20stem%20cells%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20quick%20fix%20or%20a%20panacea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20temper%20expectations%20and%20let%20patients%20know%20this%20isn't%20magic%20pixie%20dust.%20We're%20studying%20this%20under%20a%20clinical%20trial%2C%20and%20results%20do%20take%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Sampson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22748638c9-42ce-468f-a630-d10b629ec3fc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAthletes%20pioneered%20this%20trend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peyton%20Manning%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b5210c955b01c3294d06ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENFL%20superstar%20Peyton%20Manning%20received%20stem%20cell%20therapy%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%20to%20recover%20from%20a%20neck%20injury.%20He's%20one%20of%20many%20athletes%20driving%20the%20boom%20in%20experimental%20treatments.%20%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Smith%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20often%20the%20case%20with%20exclusive%20and%20experimental%20therapies%2C%20athletes%20were%20the%20real%20pioneers%20of%20this%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4236032%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2014%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2012%20NFL%20players%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeyton-manning-experimented-with-stem-cell-therapy-not-approved-in-the-united-states-before-the-season-2011-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeyton%20Manning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20received%20stem%20cell%20treatments%20(not%20approved%20by%20the%20FDA)%20to%20help%20them%20bounce%20back%20from%20various%20injuries.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorge-kittle-stem-cell-treatment-football-injuries-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENFL%20superstar%20George%20Kittle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pro%20wrestler%20Hulk%20Hogan%2C%20and%20UFC%20fighter%20TJ%20Dillashaw%20have%20all%20visited%20the%20same%20clinic%20in%20Panama%20for%20an%20injection%20of%20cells%20harvested%20from%20donated%20umbilical%20cord%20tissue.%20(Other%20athletes%20have%20had%20treatments%20involving%20their%20own%20stem%20cells%20%E2%80%94%20tennis%20great%20Rafael%20Nadal%20for%20his%20knee%20and%20back%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D073e9429345f7c3937d5ea14e704a1f92a288c3f4dab52a7c8f3b00af5bd8f25%26postID%3D66a25a57d290cb433ad34c0f%26postSlug%3Dstem-cell-injections-knee-joints-longevity-wellness-industry-bryan-johnson-2024-7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Ftennis%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F11853811%252Frafael-nadal-receive-stem-cell-treatment-back-pain%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPN%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20golfer%20Jack%20Nicklaus%20for%20his%20back%20pain%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2Fhealth%2Fjack-nicklaus-stem-cell-therapy%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESampson%20is%20frustrated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20work%20is%20inherently%20expensive%20and%20off-limits%20because%20it%20perpetuates%20a%20vicious%20cycle.%20If%20only%20a%20few%20people%20can%20do%20it%2C%20there's%20less%20opportunity%20to%20study%20how%20these%20treatments%20could%20help%20for%20aging%20and%20chronic%20diseases%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20that's%20why%20he's%20effusive%20about%20wealthy%20patients%20like%20Johnson%20and%20elite%20athletes%20who%20do%20come%20through.%20Those%20who%20have%20a%20strong%20interest%20in%20longevity%20and%20the%20resources%20to%20pursue%20it%20are%20helping%20to%20drum%20up%20interest%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hopes%20this%20buzz%20will%20drive%20research%20that%20could%20someday%20help%20treat%20or%20prevent%20multiple%20chronic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aff340ad-8c90-468b-b41c-99335df6adab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20stem%20cell%20therapy%20goes%20wrong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20is%20a%20slow%20process%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20main%20impact%20of%20this%20brewing%20interest%20is%20the%20proliferation%20of%20so-called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7002842%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erogue%20clinics%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad%2C%20making%20bold%20claims%20about%20how%20their%20unproven%20treatments%20can%20transform%20your%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDone%20with%20proper%20medical%20oversight%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1155%2F2022%2F9589600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20found%20no%20adverse%20effects%20from%20stem%20cell%20treatments%20for%20various%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20risky%20arena%2C%20though.%20Botched%20stem%20cell%20treatments%20can%20cause%20infection%2C%20blindness%20and%20excessive%20cell%20growth%2C%20which%20can%20trigger%20the%20formation%20of%20tumors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20heard%20horror%20stories%20because%20you%20go%20there%20in%20desperation%20and%20maybe%20some%20people%20will%20have%20a%20benefit%2C%20but%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%20don't%20know%20what%20they're%20getting%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaudhry%20said.%20It%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20know%20what%20exactly%20you're%20getting%2C%20how%20much%2C%20and%20whether%20it's%20been%20stored%20and%20handled%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20unknowns%20about%20the%20long-term%20effects%20of%20the%20procedures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC9659480%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests.%20Paul%20Knoepfler%2C%20professor%20and%20researcher%20at%20UC%20Davis%20School%20of%20Medicine%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D90586cabc176f0806a6067e8b2b82a45f970fad719756cf1ee6663bfff9a5c24%26postID%3D66a25a57d290cb433ad34c0f%26postSlug%3Dstem-cell-injections-knee-joints-longevity-wellness-industry-bryan-johnson-2024-7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FStem-Cells-Insiders-Paul-Knoepfler%252Fdp%252F9814508802%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStem%20Cells%3A%20An%20Insider's%20Guide%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20perceived%20benefit%20from%20stem%20cell%20treatments%20could%20be%20a%20placebo%2C%20and%20may%20cause%20patients%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20more%20evidence-based%20therapies%2C%20such%20as%20joint%20replacements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20he's%20not%20convinced%20that%20his%20approach%20of%20taking%20on%20experimental%2C%20innovative%20treatments%20is%20any%20riskier%20than%20letting%20nature%20take%20its%20course%2C%20especially%20after%20he's%20done%20his%20homework.%20%26quot%3BSomething%20could%20of%20course%20go%20wrong%2C%20but%20that's%20just%20life%20and%20something%20could%20go%20wrong%20anyways%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20risk%20is%20a%20nuanced%20conversation.%20It's%20not%20clear%20that%20this%20is%20the%20higher%20risk%20path.%20It%20may%20in%20fact%20be%20a%20lower%20risk%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e791825a-487d-492f-8165-1613c02f2795%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20takeaway%3A%20Is%20stem%20cell%20therapy%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMatthias%20Bernow%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20biotech%20company%20Cellcolabs%20that%20provided%20the%20stem%20cells%20for%20Johnson's%20procedure%2C%20has%20high%20hopes%20for%20the%20future%20of%20this%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I'm%20really%20hoping%20for%20is%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20when%20we%20go%20to%20the%20office%20for%20the%20yearly%20checkup%2C%20and%20we%20get%20our%20flu%20shot%2C%20maybe%20we'll%20also%20get%20a%20stem%20cell%20boost%20either%20to%20treat%20our%20current%20conditions%20or%20to%20delay%20the%20onset%20of%20them%2C%20to%20treat%20our%20bodies%20in%20the%20best%20possible%20way%20independently%20of%20whatever%20the%20genetic%20lottery%20gave%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20stem%20cell%20therapies%20look%20promising%20for%20vision%20loss%20or%20diabetes%2C%20experts%20largely%20agree%20that%20they%20are%20probably%20not%20a%20fountain%20of%20youth.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20high-quality%20data%20is%20needed%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20affect%20aging.%20They%20may%20not%20do%20anything%20to%20address%20more%20complex%20consequences%20of%20aging%2C%20such%20as%20neurological%20degeneration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20a%20more%20basic%20le