r%20Independence...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Raps%20Mumbai%20College%20For%20Hijab%20Ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20a%20Mumbai%20college%20which%20had%20barred%20students%20from%20wearing%20burqas%20and%20hijab%20on%20campus%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20the%20institution's%20authorities%20how%20they%20were%20empowering%20women%20by%20telling%20them%20what%20to%20wear.%20In%20a%20stinging%20observation%2C%20the%20court%20also%20remarked%20that%20it%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20such%20bans%20were%20imposed%20even%20so%20many%20years%20after%20Independence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20nine%20girl%20students%20against%20the%20ban%20on%20burqas%2C%20hijab%2C%20niqab%2C%20caps%2C%20stoles%20and%20badges%20imposed%20by%20the%20NG%20Acharya%20%26amp%3B%20DK%20Marathe%20College%20in%20Mumbai's%20Chembur%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20PV%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20partially%20stayed%20the%20order.%20It%20said%20hijabs%2C%20caps%20and%20badges%20would%20be%20allowed%20and%20added%20that%20it%20hoped%20that%20the%20order%20would%20not%20be%20misused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20hearing%20began%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Madhavi%20Divan%2C%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20college%2C%20said%20that%20if%20the%20petitioners%20were%20allowed%20to%20wear%20hijabs%20and%20burqas%2C%20other%20students%20would%20come%20wearing%20saffron%20shawls%20to%20make%20a%20political%20point%20and%20it%20did%20not%20want%20that%20to%20happen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20you%20ban%20girls%20wearing%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebindi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Etilak%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20for%20the%20college%20said%20that%20there%20were%20441%20students%20from%20the%20community%20in%20the%20college%20and%20when%20a%20girl%20wears%20a%20veil%20or%20an%20article%20of%20clothing%20like%20that%2C%20it%20creates%20a%20b