20the%20beach%20in%20St.%20Bart's.%3Cp%3EKelly%20Magyarics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGlittering%20Saint%20Bart's%20is%20full%20of%20fancy%20spots%2C%20with%20a%20yacht-filled%20harbor%2C%20designer%20shops%20along%20the%20pristine%20streets%20of%20Gustavia%20(the%20island's%20capital)%2C%20and%20luxurious%20hotels%20like%20the%20Hotel%20Manapany%20and%20Eden%20Rock.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20a%20lively%20day-drinking%20scene%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnikki-beach-ceo-crazy-requests-from-vip-guests-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENikki%20Beach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20destination%20that's%20attracted%20celebrity%20guests%20like%20Mariah%20Carey%2C%20and%20restaurants%20with%20menus%20and%20wine%20lists%20to%20rival%20any%20Parisian%20hot%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20multimillionaire%20to%20soak%20in%20the%20island's%20beguiling%20swankiness.%20During%20my%20visit%2C%20I%20spent%20an%20afternoon%20on%20a%20catamaran%20ride%20and%20did%20some%20window%20shopping%20at%20the%20home-design%20store%20Maison%20P%C3%A9lican.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisitors%20can%20also%20find%20elevated%20cuisine%20at%20various%20price%20points%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20tuna%20poke%20and%20chilled%20ros%C3%A9%20from%20Ti'%20Corail%20on%20a%20laid-back%20beach%2C%20and%20it%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20most%20surprised%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-warm-places-to-stop-on-cruise-crew-member-reveals-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20local%20beaches%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20the%20sandy%20Gouverneur%20Beach%20and%20secluded%20Colombier%20Beach%2C%20a%20spot%20accessible%20only%20after%20a%20steep%20(but%20worth%20it)%20hike.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20Francophile%20who%20adores%20fabulous%20food%20and%20an%20upscale%20feel%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20Saint%20Bart's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESaint%20Martin%20is%20the%20perfect%20destination%20for%20plane%20and%20food%20enthusiasts.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20beach%20with%20deep-blue%20water%20next%20to%20a%20pathway%20surrounded%20bt%20palm%20trees%20and%20greenery%20and%20houses%20and%20mountains%20in%20the%20background.%20A%20blue%20sky%20with%20clouds%20overlooks%20the%20island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c3f0ad1c84a0eaca7fc9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESaint%20Martin%20had%20plenty%20of%20things%20to%20do%2C%20like%20visiting%20Maho%20Beach.%3Cp%3EKelly%20Magyarics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESaint%20Martin%20is%20split%20into%20two%20distinct%20French%20and%20Dutch%20sides.%20I%20thought%20the%20French%20side%20had%20a%20quiet%2C%20relaxed%20vibe%20during%20my%20visit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20laid%20on%20the%20beach%20at%20Orient%20Bay%20(referred%20to%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.st-martin.org%2Fus%2Ffor-a-truly-friendly-experience%2Forient-bay-beach-discover-the-saint-tropez-of-the-caribbean%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaint-Tropez%20of%20the%20Caribbean%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20shopped%20at%20the%20luxury%20boutiques%20in%20Marigot%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20French%20Collectivity%20on%20Saint%20Martin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20Dutch%20side%20much%20livelier%20as%20I%20clubbed%20at%20the%20Soggy%20Dollar%20Bar%20in%20Simpson%20Bay%20and%20sipped%20rum%20cocktails%20while%20watching%20the%20sunset%20at%20The%20Rusty%20Parrot.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20is%20also%20the%20ultimate%20destination%20for%20aviation%20geeks%2C%20as%20the%20Princess%20Juliana%20International%20Airport%20is%20steps%20away%20from%20Maho%20Beach.%20I%20spent%20hours%20watching%20planes%20fly%20directly%20above%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisitors%20can%20also%20island%20hop%20to%20nearby%20Saint%20Bart's%20and%20Anguill