0living%20proof%20that%20you%20can%20have%20both%20%E2%80%94%20a%20long%20and%20full%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFerrari%20is%20nothing%20if%20not%20resilient.%20She%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-testing-positive-covid-19-changed-from-2020-2021-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econtracted%20COVID-19%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20April%202020%20%E2%80%94%20during%20the%20particularly%20fraught%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20while%20she%20spent%2026%20days%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20some%20of%20which%20she%20was%20only%20semi-conscious%2C%20she%20survived%20the%20illness%20unscathed.%20Ferrari's%20husband%20and%20most%20of%20her%20lifelong%20friends%20died%20years%20ago.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Ferrari%20still%20lives%20on%20her%20own%20in%20the%20independent%20living%20section%20of%20a%20retirement%20community.%20She%20drove%20her%20own%20car%20until%20she%20was%2080%20years%20old.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20enjoying%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20I%20have%20a%20pleasant%20little%20apartment%2C%20and%20my%20daughter%20lives%20nearby.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d91ae2a8-fd81-4ec7-991b-6ef03e7c2af4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20a%20perpetual%20student%20has%20given%20her%20purpose%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFerrari%20graduated%20from%20The%20College%20of%20New%20Rochelle%20(which%20has%20since%20closed)%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20English%20in%201950%20%E2%80%94%20a%20time%20when%20very%20few%20women%20were%20pursuing%20undergraduate%20degrees.%20Later%2C%20she%20went%20on%20to%20receive%20not%20one%20but%20two%20graduate%20degrees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20always%20looked%20to%20my%20great%20aunt%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20have%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20purpo