e%20said%20drivers%20%26quot%3Bare%20lucky%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20receive%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20an%20Uber%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BUber's%20take%20rate%20has%20remained%20largely%20flat%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20amount%20of%20the%20rider%20fare%20that%20goes%20toward%20local%20government%20taxes%20and%20fees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20commercial%20auto%20insurance%2C%20has%20increased%20significantly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyft%20says%20its%20drivers%20are%20guaranteed%20to%20earn%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-earnings-gig-driver-rider-payments-uber-hourly-pay-stock-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E70%25%20of%20rider%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20week%2C%20after%20external%20fees%20like%20local%20taxes%20and%20government-mandated%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20heard%20lots%20of%20feedback%20around%20consistent%20themes%20%E2%80%94%20earnings%2C%20deactivations%2C%20and%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20taking%20action%20to%20address%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Risher%2C%20Lyft's%20CEO%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20companies%20refute%20some%20of%20the%20findings%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-doordash-drivers-earn-below-minimum-wage-tips-study-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUC%20Berkeley%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20May%20found%20that%20many%20gig%20drivers%20earn%20less%20than%20their%20area's%20minimum%20wage%20after%20accounting%20for%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20drivers%2C%20on%20average%2C%20make%20more%20than%20%2430%20an%20hour%20while%20active%20in%20the%20app.%20In%20February%2C%20Lyft%20said%20the%20typical%20US%20driver%20who%20used%20a%20personal%20vehicle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-uber-lyft-drivers-make-per-ride-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearned%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20%2431%20per%20engaged%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%2423%20an%20hour%20after%20accounting%20for%20expenses%20like%20gas%20and%20maintenance.%20However%2C%20many%20drivers%20have%20told%20BI%20has%20spoken%20to%20said%20they%20earn%20less%20than%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-driving-for-uber-worth-it-declining-pay-more-competition-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-time%20Uber%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Cleveland%20who%20has%20driven%20since%202017%2C%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20quit%20but%20has%20few%20other%20options.%20He%20made%20%24109%2C000%20in%20driver%20earnings%20last%20year%20but%20only%20took%20home%20%2417%2C000%20after%20Uber's%20commission%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20maintenance%20fees.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20to%20work%20nearly%20double%20the%20hours%20to%20make%20the%20same%20amount%20in%20a%20week%20he%20made%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20have%20also%20reported%20lower%20or%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-you-tip-uber-lyft-driver-doordash-rideshare-food-delivery-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einconsistent%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20with%20UC%20Berkeley%20finding%20that%20customers%20were%20three%20times%20as%20likely%20to%20tip%20delivery%20drivers%20as%20rideshare%20drivers.%20Uber%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20tipping%20frequency%20and%20average%20tip%20size%20have%20both%20roughly%20doubled%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260a7044f-78e6-4e5f-905b-8d91790539e8%5C%22%3ESome%20drivers%20worry%20about%20their%20safety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAvedian%20said%20many%20drivers%20also%20have%20concerns%20about%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20day%20goes%20by%20that%20we%20don't%20hear%20about%20carjacking%20of%20Uber%20or%20L