m%2Fdriving-and-delivering%2Farticle%2Frecord-my-ride---frequently-asked-questions%3FnodeId%3D7f86cc51-2c3e-4888-8dc1-0ac2b6337b92%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERecord%20My%20Ride%3C%2Fa%3E%20feature%20that%20turns%20a%20driver's%20phone%20into%20a%20dashcam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Lyft%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20has%20an%20around-the-clock%20safety%20response%20team%20that%20can%20be%20contacted%20via%20phone%20or%20chat%2C%20a%20trauma-informed%20care%20team%20with%20specialized%20training%2C%20and%20a%20location-sharing%20option%20drivers%20can%20use%20to%20ensure%20loved%20ones%20know%20where%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e74002a0-804e-40d7-9741-ed3ee1910a1d%5C%22%3EDrivers%20worry%20about%20being%20wrongly%20deactivated%20%E2%80%94%20and%20don't%20receive%20enough%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAvedian%20believes%20many%20drivers%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-avoiding-deactivation-or-firing-uber-doordash-lyft-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrongly%20deactivated%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Uber%20platform.%20When%20drivers%20try%20to%20contact%20Uber%20to%20discuss%20their%20deactivations%20or%20other%20issues%2C%20he%20said%20the%20company's%20driver%20support%20system%20and%20agents%20are%20often%20unhelpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20can%20be%20deactivated%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uber.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fdrive%2Fsafety%2Fdeactivations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20reasons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20low%20platform%20rating%2C%20a%20failed%20background%20check%2C%20an%20expired%20license%2C%20and%20customer%20accusations%20of%20safety%20issues.%20However%2C%20Avedian%20said%20drivers%20are%20sometimes%20deactivated%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bfraudulent%20rider%20claims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Lavender%2C%20an%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20driver%20in%20Colorado%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteacher-quit-to-become-full-time-uber-lyft-driver-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20was%20deactivated%20from%20the%20Uber%20app%20for%20three%20days%20after%20a%20customer%20filed%20a%20complaint%20saying%20that%20his%20appearance%20and%20smell%20made%20them%20suspect%20he%20was%20intoxicated.%20Lavender%20said%20he%20was%20eventually%20cleared%20by%20Uber%20following%20a%20brief%20investigation%20and%20had%20his%20account%20reactivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStories%20of%20permanent%20deactivation%20do%20scare%20me%20and%20make%20me%20not%20want%20to%20rely%20solely%20on%20this%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20drivers%20have%20a%20harder%20time%20getting%20their%20deactivations%20reversed.%20An%20Uber%20Eats%20driver%20in%20Oregon%20was%20making%20a%20delivery%20when%20the%20customer%20changed%20the%20dropoff%20location%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-gig-workers-are-fighting-against-sudden-account-deactivations-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20new%20destination%20turned%20a%2010-minute%20trip%20into%20a%20one-hour%20one%2C%20so%20he%20contacted%20Uber%20Eats%20support%20to%20try%20to%20cancel%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20support%20agent%20approved%20the%20cancellation%2C%20but%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20his%20account%20was%20deactivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20it%20says%20my%20account%20is%20under%20investigation%20for%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20says%20'fraud.'%20It%20doesn't%20give%20any%20details.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20months%20of%20exchanging%20messages%20with%20agents%2C%20he%20said%20his%20account%20was%20eventually%20reactivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20last%20year%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww