%20bail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Friday%20morning%20-%20nearly%2018%20months%20after%20the%C2%A0ex-Delhi%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20In%20a%20powerful%20verdict%20the%20court%20said%20he%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bspeedy%20trial%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20a%20rejection%20now%20would%20force%20him%20to%20work%20his%20way%20back%20up%20the%20system.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20like%20making%20him%20play%20snakes%20and%20ladders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20matter%20pertaining%20to%20the%20life%20and%20liberty%20of%20a%20citizen%20-%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sacrosanct%20rights%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20Constitution%20-%20a%20citizen%20cannot%20be%20made%20to%20run%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20February%2026%2C%202023%2C%20and%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20later.%20He%20has%20now%20been%20granted%20bail%20in%20both%20cases%2C%20with%20an%20irate%20Supreme%20Court%20stating%20he%20cannot%20stay%20in%20jail%20indefinitely%20while%20the%20prosecution%20works%20to%20an%20unconfirmed%20trial%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20also%20said%20keeping%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20in%20jailed%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bunlimited%20time%26quot%3B%2C%20without%20a%20trial%2C%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20his%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncarceration%20of%2018%20months...%20Trial%20not%20having%20even%20commenced%20and%20appellant%20has%20been%20deprived%20of%20right%20to%20speedy%20trial%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20said%20as%20he%20asked%20tough%20questions%20of%20the%20lower%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeeping%20appellant%20behind%20bars%20for%20unlimited%20ti