s%20expected%20to%20walk%20out%20of%20jail%20today%20or%20tomorrow.%20The%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20said%20Mr%20Sisodia%20would%20be%20released%20later%20today%20or%20tomorrow%20once%20the%20formalities%20at%20Tihar%20jail%20are%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20also%20expressed%20optimism%20about%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20court's%20order%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20order%20will%20significantly%20benefit%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20case%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20at%20Tihar%20Jail%20indicated%20that%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20currently%20held%20in%20Jail%20Number%201%2C%20would%20likely%20exit%20through%20Gate%20Number%203%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20used%20for%20the%20release%20of%20inmates%20from%20that%20specific%20jail%20block.%20However%2C%20if%20there%20are%20any%20security%20concerns%2C%20alternate%20arrangements%20might%20be%20made.%20The%20exact%20timing%20of%20the%20AAP%20leader's%20release%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20processing%20of%20the%20bail%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20standard%20procedure%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20bail%20order%20will%20first%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20Court%2C%20where%20the%20necessary%20bail%20bonds%20and%20other%20conditions%20will%20be%20fulfilled.%20Once%20these%20formalities%20are%20completed%2C%20the%20bail%20order%20will%20be%20forwarded%20to%20Tihar%20Jail%20for%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20today%20emphasized%20that%20Mr%20Sisodia's%20prolonged%20imprisonment%20without%20a%20trial%20had%20deprived%20him%20of%20his%20fundamental%20right%20to%20a%20speedy%20trial.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20matter%20of%20liberty%2C%20every%20day%20counts%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20Justice%20Gavai%2C%20underlining%20the%20urgency%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bail%20order%20came%20as%20a%20hug