was%20disqualified%20from%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20due%20to%20a%20weight%20issue%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20final.%20The%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20has%20appealed%20for%20the%20Phogat%20to%20be%20given%20a%20joint%20silver%20medal%20for%20her%20stellar%20show%20at%20the%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20or%20CAS%20is%20an%20international%20body%20established%20in%201984%20to%20settle%20disputes%20in%20sport%20through%20arbitration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarish%20Salve%2C%20former%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20and%20King's%20Counsel%2C%20has%20confirmed%20that%20he%20has%20been%20engaged%20by%20the%20IOA%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fvinesh-phogats-plea-against-olympic-disqualification-accepted-by-cas-6298194%5C%22%3Erepresent%20Phogat%20in%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalve%20was%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20from%201999%20to%202002.%20He%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20India's%20top%20lawyers%2C%20known%20for%20his%20exceptional%20expertise%20in%20constitutional%2C%20commercial%2C%20and%20arbitration%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20notable%20cases%20Harish%20Salve's%20fought%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkulbhushan-jadhav-case-pakistan-misusing-this-court-international-court-of-justice-for-propaganda-in-1995275%5C%22%3EKulbhushan%20Jadhav%3C%2Fa%3E%20Case%20(2017)%3A%20He%20represented%20India%20at%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Kulbhushan%20Jadhav%2C%20an%20Indian%20national%20sentenced%20to%20death%20in%20Pakistan.%20Salve%20successfully%20argued%20for%20a%20stay%20on%20Jadhav's%20execution.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERatan%20Tata%20vs%20Cyrus%20Mistry%20(2016)%3A%20Mr%20Salve%20represented%20Ratan%20Tata%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20against%20Cyrus%20Mis