e-the-lawyer-fighting-to-get-vinesh-phogat-olympic-medal-6298275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20Agrees%20To%20Debate%20Kamala%20Harris%3A%20What%20Latest%20Polls%20Suggest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20agreed%20to%20debate%20his%20Democratic%20counterpart%20Kamala%20Harris%20on%20September%2010.%20The%20showdown%20is%20set%20to%20be%20hosted%20by%20ABC%2C%20with%20additional%20debates%20proposed%20for%20September%204%20and%20September%2025%20on%20Fox%20and%20NBC%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20face-off%20between%20the%20two%20rivals%2C%20with%20polls%20indicating%20a%20closely%20contested%20race.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20vs%20Harris%3A%20What%20polls%20predict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIpsos%20poll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20Ipsos%20poll%20published%20on%20August%209%2C%20shows%20Kamala%20Harris%20leading%20Donald%20Trump%2042%20per%20cent%20to%2037%20per%20cent%20for%20the%20November%205%20elections.%20This%20shows%20growth%20in%20her%20popularity%20since%20a%20July%2022-23%20Reuters%2FIpsos%20survey%2C%20which%20found%20her%20up%2037%20per%20cent%20to%2034%20per%20cent%20over%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20poll%2C%20Ipsos%20found%20Harris%20leading%20Trump%2042%20per%20cent%20to%2040%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20seven%20states%20where%20the%20election%20was%20closest%20in%202020%20-%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Nevada%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Pennsylvania%20and%20Wisconsin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouGov%20poll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CBS%2FYouGov%20poll%20released%20on%20August%204%20shows%20Kamala%20Harris%20levelling%20up%20with%20Donald%20Trump.%20She%20has%20erased%20Trump's%20growing%20lead%20since%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20dropped%20his%20reelection%20bid.%20The%20