simon-robinson-british-man-missing-after-taking-flight-from-bangkok-13193455%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsimon-robinson-british-man-missing-after-taking-flight-from-bangkok-13193455%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MBA%20Couple%20Quit%20Corporate%20Life%20to%20%E2%80%98Move%20to%20The%20Hills%E2%80%99%2C%20Start%20Dreamy%20Organic%20Cafe%20in%20Uttarakhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20beat%20down%20on%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Barapullah%20flyover%20in%202017%2C%20a%20couple%20found%20themselves%20caught%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20decisive%20clarity.%20Amit%2C%20an%20employee%20at%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20confided%20in%20his%20wife%20Shipra%2C%20an%20advertising%20professional%20at%20Outlook%20Magazine%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20anymore.%20I%E2%80%99m%20resigning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20asked%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20resign%20as%20well%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShipra%20nodded.%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20do%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20ahead%20was%20unclear%2C%20but%20their%20minds%20were%20made.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20knew%20we%20were%20going%20to%20follow%20our%20hearts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Shipra%20now%20reflects%20that%20perhaps%20they%20should%20have%20made%20this%20move%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20childhood%20friends%20had%20been%20craving%20something%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20nine-to-five%20routine.%20Both%20had%20a%20passion%20for%20the%20natural%20world%20and%20organising%20forest%20trips.%20And%20they%20were%20both%20fond%20of%20food.%20They%20began%20to%20wonder%20if%20they%20could%20shape%20their%20lives%20around%20this%20shared%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaving%20their%20careers%20in%20Delhi%20behind%2C%20with%20no%20back-up%20plan%2C%20Amit%20Kumar%20Srivastava%20and%20Shipra%20Mohan%20Sinha%20moved%20to%20Devikhal%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20where%20they%20had%20already%20set%20up%20a%20quain