0for%20which%20labour%20is%20required%2C%20and%20whether%20accommodation%20and%20food%20are%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20can%20access%20these%20details%20and%20call%20the%20job%20poster%20directly%20to%20express%20their%20interest.%20On%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20side%2C%20they%20add%20details%20like%20their%20skills%2C%20past%20experiences%2C%20and%20minimum%20wages.%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20is%20working%20to%20make%20digital%20labour%20cards%20for%20these%20workers%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20them%20with%20an%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20planning%20to%20give%20incentives%20based%20on%20their%20performance%20to%20boost%20their%20morale.%20This%20is%20our%20effort%20to%20organise%20the%20informal%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Noida%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20get%2010%20connections%20for%20free%2C%20post%20which%20they%20pay%20a%20subscription%20fee.%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20is%20free%20for%20workers.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20partnering%20with%20institutes%20to%20provide%20upskilling%20courses%20for%20the%20workers%2C%20as%20there%20is%20a%20dearth%20of%20skilled%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrawan%20Kumar%20from%20Darbhanga%20has%20been%20free%20of%20worry%20for%20the%20past%20year.%20He%20was%20employed%20by%20a%20builder%20in%20Jodhpur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20on%20a%20long-term%20contract.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20earned%20in%20one%20year%20what%20I%20used%20to%20earn%20in%20three%20years.%20We%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20heat%20daily%20looking%20for%20jobs.%20When%20one%20contract%20is%20about%20to%20end%2C%20we%20can%20choose%20the%20next%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20projects%20last%20for%20at%20least%2021%20days%2C%20according%20to%20Chandrashekhar.%20He%20claims%20that%20there%20are%20500%20to%201%2C000%20jobs%20posted%20daily%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzhar%20Ansari%2C%20wh